ev.net/images/Furnace-Repair-Minneapolis-MN-300x225.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />At Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air, we ensure that every Minneapolis resident experiences “Comfort to Every Degree” through our services for furnace repair. We understand that having a furnace out of commission is never a convenience, which is why we offer emergency furnace repair to each of our customers in Minneapolis. In addition to helping you feel comfort through the air that enters your home, we want you to feel comfortable with the service we provide and with the technicians that are in your Minneapolis home.\r\n\r\nFor this reason, we only employ techs who have passed background checks and are the most highly qualified in the industry for emergency furnace repair or any other furnace issues in Minneapolis.\r\n<h2>Our Heating Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnaces\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnaces/\">Furnaces</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-repair/\">Furnace Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Replacement\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-replacement/\">Furnace Replacement</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-maintenance/\">Furnace Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-installation/\">Furnace Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Heat Exchangers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/heat-exchangers/\">Heat Exchangers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Heat Pumps\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/heat-pumps/\">Heat Pumps</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Heating\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/zone-heating/\">Zone Heating</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Signs You Need Furnace Repair in Minneapolis</h2>\r\nIt’s not always easy to spot a broken furnace, but with our tips, it will be a lot easier. The following are some signs that may indicate that a furnace repair is in order for you:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>Noise.</b> Most furnaces make some type of noise, but if you hear abnormal groaning, whining, or banging, it may need a repair or two.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Cold</b>. If your home is still cold after you have cranked the thermostat up over and over again, that is a sign that either your thermostat is broken, your ducts are leaking, or perhaps even that your pilot light is not working.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Bills</b>. If your electric bills have sky rocketed, but you haven’t changed your habits in regards to the thermostat temperature too much, it could need a repair.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Sickness</b>. Sometimes a faulty furnace can cause your family to become ill. Whether you are sick more than usual, or if there is a recurring issue with breathing-related troubles, it could be the furnace.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Age</b>. A furnace that is over fifteen years old is more likely to need to be repaired or replaced, and you should have a professional at Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air take a look at yours to determine the necessary action.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Other Minneapolis Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair in Minneapolis, MN\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/service-area/air-conditioner-repair-in-minneapolis-mn/\">Air Conditioner Repair in Minneapolis, MN</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Contact Us Today</h2>\r\nFor more information on emergency furnace repair in Minneapolis, contact the professionals with the most experience in the industry. <strong>Call Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air at 972-647-0099 or fill out our online form, and let’s get your furnace repair in Minneapolis started.</strong>','Furnace Repair in Minneapolis, MN','','publish','open','open','','furnace-repair-in-minneapolis-mn','','','2013-10-25 18:06:42','2013-10-25 18:06:42','',156,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=195',0,'page','',0),(5,1,'2013-08-14 05:57:00','2013-08-14 05:57:00','<h1>About Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air</h1>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-801 ali