der for you:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>Noise.</b> Most furnaces make some type of noise, but if you hear abnormal groaning, whining, or banging, it may need a repair or two.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Cold</b>. If your home is still cold after you have cranked the thermostat up over and over again, that is a sign that either your thermostat is broken, your ducts are leaking, or perhaps even that your pilot light is not working.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Bills</b>. If your electric bills have sky rocketed, but you haven’t changed your habits in regards to the thermostat temperature too much, it could need a repair.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Sickness</b>. Sometimes a faulty furnace can cause your family to become ill. Whether you are sick more than usual, or if there is a recurring issue with breathing-related troubles, it could be the furnace.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Age</b>. A furnace that is over fifteen years old is more likely to need to be repaired or replaced, and you should have a professional at Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air take a look at yours to determine the necessary action.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Other Lakeville Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair in Lakeville, MN\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/service-area/air-conditioner-repair-in-lakeville-mn/\">Air Conditioner Repair in Lakeville, MN</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Contact Us Today</h2>\r\nFor more information on emergency furnace repair in Lakeville, contact the professionals with the most experience in the industry. <strong>Call Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air at 972-647-0099 or fill out our online form, and let’s get your furnace repair started.</strong>','Furnace Repair in Lakeville, MN','','publish','open','open','','furnace-repair-in-lakeville-mn','','','2013-10-11 15:39:39','2013-10-11 15:39:39','',156,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=227',0,'page','',0),(117,1,'2013-08-22 07:01:17','2013-08-22 07:01:17','','Air Conditioning','','inherit','open','open','','7-revision-v1','','','2013-08-22 07:01:17','2013-08-22 07:01:17','',