s\" href=\"/financing/\">Financing plans</a> are available as well.\r\n<h2>Call Us Today</h2>\r\nBlue Ox has extensive experience in zone heating and cooling systems and can install yours today. Our professional team of technicians is able to deliver the service you need to reduce your energy usage. We are available 24/7 for all of your heating and air needs.\r\n\r\n<strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact us</a> at 952-647-0099 for more information. Let us provide comfort to every degree of your home.</strong>','Zone Systems','','publish','open','open','','zone-heating-cooling','','','2013-10-11 14:03:46','2013-10-11 14:03:46','',6,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=269',0,'page','',0),(270,1,'2013-09-13 19:56:29','2013-09-13 19:56:29','','Zone Heating','','inherit','open','open','','269-revision-v1','','','2013-09-13 19:56:29','2013-09-13 19:56:29','',269,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/269-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(271,1,'2013-09-13 19:56:46','2013-09-13 19:56:46','Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.','Cooling','','inherit','open','open','','7-revision-v1','','','2013-09-13 19:56:46','2013-09-13 19:56:46','',7,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(272,1,'2013-09-13 19:56:57','2013-09-13 19:56:57','<h1>Air Conditioner Units</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-1086\" title=\"Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air Conditioning\" alt=\"Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air Conditioning\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Blue-Ox-Van-Worker-300x200.jpg\" width=\"270\" height=\"180\" />There is nothing like enjoying a hot summer day knowing that you can return to your comfortably cooled and dehumidified home. At Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air, we sell only the finest quality air conditioner units from the best manufacturers in the business. Our 200 years of combined experience in the business of heating and cooling makes us the best candidates for all of your cooling needs.\r\n<h2>Our Air Conditioner Services</h2>\r\nOur dependable team of professionals is available to service your air conditioners, Blue Ox specializes in:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe are so confident in our services that we guarantee your complete satisfaction in everything we do.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How Air Conditioners Work</h2>\r\nAs you sit in your cool house, your home air conditioner units are working to direct the hot air from within your home back to the outside. The cool air blowing out of your vents is created as the central air conditioning unit sends warm air over the evaporator coil. The evaporator coil consists of a series of cold pipes that are filled with refrigerant. As the refrigerant absorbs heat from the passing air, it turns into a gas. It then moves outside the house, gives up its heat, and returns to a liquid state. A compressor in the outdoor unit is responsible for moving the refrigerant between the coils. Amazingly, this entire process is able to function to bring us the cool and refreshing air that we crave on a hot day.\r\n<h2>Licensed Professionals</h2>\r\nAt Blue Ox Heating and Air, we are proud of our highly-skilled team of professionals. Each technician undergoes a rigorous background check before being hired onto the team. We work hard to uphold our exceptional reputation as being the finest heating and cooling company in the Twin Cities and Minneapolis areas. Let our trained team install your residential air conditioner units today.\r\n<h2>We Provide Comfort to Every Degree</h2>\r\nAt Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air, we believe that you have the right to feel comfortable in your home. We strive to provide you the best heating and cooling services available. <strong>Call us today at 952-641-0099 or <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contact us online</a> for a free evaluation of your air conditioners.</strong>','Air Conditioners','','publish','open','open','','air-conditioners','','','2013-10-25 16:53:00','2013-10-25 16:53:00','',7,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=272',0,'page','',0),(273,1,'2013-09-13 19:56:57','2013-09-13 19:56:57','','Air Conditioners','','inherit','open','open','','272-revision-v1','','','2013-09-13 19:56:57','2013-09-13 19:56:57','',272,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/272-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(274,1,'2013-09-13 19:57:14','2013-09-13 19:57:14','<h1>Affordable Air Conditioner Repair</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-967\" title=\"Air Conditioner Repair \" alt=\"Air Conditioner Repair \" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Furnace-Repair-HVAC-Technician-214x300.jpg\" width=\"193\" height=\"270\" />When your air conditioner breaks, you know immediately. Often times, it seems as though air conditioners decide to fail on the hottest day of the year. Luckily, Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air is available for air conditioner repair in the Minneapolis and Twin Cities areas. Our experienced technicians will have your air conditioner working again in no time. We offer affordable professional services for our valued customers. Your satisfaction is guaranteed.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Common Air Conditioner Problems</h2>\r\nThe air conditioning process relies heavily on specific conditions to be met in order to operate correctly. There are a number of problems indicating that you may need an air conditioner repair, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Refrigerant Leak</strong>: If you have a leak in your sir conditioning system, the refrigerant charge (amount of refrigerant in the system) may become too low to keep up with the cooling needs of your home.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Change in Outdoor Airflow</strong>: If the condenser experiences reduced air flow or higher outdoor temperatures, the capacity of the air conditioner may become compromised.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Frozen Evaporator Coil</strong>: When the airflow through the evaporator is restricted, the coil will likely freeze. In time, a frozen coil will damage the compressor.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Leaking Ducts</strong>: Even if your air conditioning unit is in perfect operating condition, you can still lose up to 40% of your energy if there is a leak in your ductwork. Our team is specially trained to check for duct insulation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMany of these situations can be avoided by calling Blue Ox to schedule routine maintenance for your air conditioner.\r\n<h2>Financing Available</h2>\r\nWe are pleased to accept all major credit cards, cash and checks for our services. We even offer convenient financing options on approved credit. Give us a call and we can go over all of your payment options.\r\n<h2>Let’s Get Started!</h2>\r\n<strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air</a> today for professional air conditioner repair at 952-641-0099.</strong> We provide innovative solutions to your toughest cooling problems. We’ll get started right away on your AC repair.','Air Conditioner Repair','','publish','open','open','','air-conditioner-repair','','','2013-10-24 18:55:35','2013-10-24 18:55:35','',7,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=274',0,'page','',0),(275,1,'2013-09-13 19:57:14','2013-09-13 19:57:14','','Air Conditioner Repair','','inherit','open','open','','274-revision-v1','','','2013-09-13 19:57:14','2013-09-13 19:57:14','',274,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/274-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(276,1,'2013-09-13 19:57:26','2013-09-13 19:57:26','<h1>Expert Air Conditioner Installation</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-734\" title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" alt=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Air-Conditioner-Installation-200x300.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"270\" />Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air is the smart choice for air conditioner installation in Minneapolis, MN, and the Twin Cities area. We carefully select our technicians in order to offer each client the most highly skilled and trained air conditioning experts in the industry. We understand that affordable AC installation services don’t have to come at the cost of the quality of work we present, and we’re proud to provide exceptional customer service, convenience, and comfort.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Is My Air Conditioner Inefficient?</h2>\r\nMany homeowners don’t realize that their air conditioning system is inefficient and costing them money. Speak with a Blue Ox representative about new air conditioner installation if you have noticed any of the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>High Energy Bills</strong> – While electricity rates may fluctuate each month, if your energy bills have skyrocketed there may be something wrong with your unit. Our technicians will verify that you are using the correctly sized unit for your property, and take you through a list of possible scenarios that may be the cause of your large power bills. We’ll establish a strategy to fix the issues, and provide you with fast, top of the line AC installation services.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Irregular Cooling</strong> – If one room of the house is sweltering while the other feels like a freezer, your AC is likely operating inefficiently. Your system may need to be rebalanced or replaced. One of our professional HVAC technicians will evaluate the