',276,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/276-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(278,1,'2013-09-13 19:57:56','2013-09-13 19:57:56','<h1>Seasonal AC Maintenance</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-869\" title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance \" alt=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance \" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Air-Conditioner-Repair-Plymouth-MN-300x199.jpg\" width=\"270\" height=\"179\" />At Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air we are proud to offer exceptional air conditioner maintenance services to those in Minneapolis, MN, and the Twin Cities area. Annual upkeep of your air conditioner is crucial in order to extend the life of the system and ensure that it is consistently cost-efficient. We strive to preserve our reputation as a company that puts our clients’ comfort first, and our friendly technicians are trained to handle all of your AC maintenance needs.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Air Conditioner Maintenance You Can Do at Home</h2>\r\nWhile routine, professional assessments of your HVAC unit are essential in order to safeguard that your system will effectively operate during the warmer months, proper air conditioner maintenance starts at home. The following tips can be used to help maintain your system:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Change Furnace Filter</strong> – Dirt can build up in the system if the furnace filter is not changed frequently. For those with allergies or asthma, it is best to change the filter every month. A clean filter will promote better air quality and a more efficient system.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Clean Vents</strong> – Warm air is drawn in, cooled, and delivered to your home through the vents. Over time dust will settle on them and should be cleaned off several times a year.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Brush Condenser Coil</strong> – A clean outdoor unit (condenser) produces cooler air while using less energy. Sometime in the spring, use a vacuum, brush or hose to clean the condenser. Contact an AC maintenance technician if you are unsure how to properly perform this step.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf your system is performing erratically or you aren’t comfortable with doing systematic air conditioner maintenance on your own, Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air will be pleased to assist you.\r\n<h2>Scheduled AC Maintenance Saves You Time</h2>\r\nAir conditioner emergencies pop up when you least expect them and usually when they are most inconvenient. Regular maintenance of your air conditioning unit keeps you in control of your schedule and helps you catch minor issues before they become a threat to your time and money.\r\n\r\n<strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact Blue Ox</a> by calling 952-641-0099 to schedule your AC maintenance today.</strong>','Air Conditioner Maintenance','','publish','open','open','','air-conditioner-maintenance','','','2013-10-24 18:56:48','2013-10-24 18:56:48','',7,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=278',0,'page','',0),(279,1,'2013-09-13 19:57:56','2013-09-13 19:57:56','','Air Conditioner Maintenance','','inherit','open','open','','278-revision-v1','','','2013-09-13 19:57:56','2013-09-13 19:57:56','',278,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/278-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(280,1,'2013-09-13 19:58:10','2013-09-13 19:58:10','<h1>High Velocity Air Conditioners</h1>\r\n<a href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Blue-Ox-HVAC-Technician1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1148\" alt=\"Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air \" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Blue-Ox-HVAC-Technician1-200x300.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /></a>The technicians at Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air are experts in the field and understand the intricacies of the weather in Minneapolis, MN, and the Twin Cities area. We keep up to date on the newest systems available and are always prepared to offer property owners the best service possible. Your needs are our priority, so we make sure to get the job done right\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How High Velocity Air Conditioning Works</h2>\r\nA high velocity air conditioner draws air over cooling coils instead of pushing it like traditional AC units do. Most mini-duct air conditioning units use coils with a large surface area which creates colder air currents, thus reducing the costs of running the system while also increasing efficiency.\r\n\r\nConsider the benefits of using a high velocity unit in your property:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Consistent Airflow</strong> – The circulation system of a high velocity central air conditioning system is designed to create even airflow in every room of the house. They generally come with many vents that are appropriately placed throughout the property to better facilitate those efforts.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Fast &amp; Efficient</strong> – Using half of the airflow of a conventional AC unit, a high velocity air conditioner can quickly cool a room. They also typically eliminate around 30 percent more of the air’s moisture than a standard system can.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Smaller Ducts</strong> – Mini-duct air conditioners don’t require extensive renovation or bulky ducts. This is a benefit for those who have older homes without an existing central HVAC unit, as well as homeowners who cannot afford the high costs of renovating their home to accommodate them.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Making the Switch to High Velocity Air Conditioning is Easy</h2>\r\nSwitching from a conventional HVAC unit to a mini-duct cooling system is easy. The small ducts are only two inches in diameter and can fit easily inside walls and below floors or other tight spaces. Therefore, it is not necessary to build soffits or creative hiding places to conceal metal ductwork, thus maintaining the integrity of your home.\r\n\r\n<strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air</a> today at 952-641-0099 to speak with an air conditioning professional to gain more insight on the benefits of installing a high velocity air conditioner in your home.</strong>','High Velocity Cooling','','publish','open','closed','','high-velocity-air-conditioners','','','2013-10-25 18:12:25','2013-10-25 18:12:25','',7,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=280',0,'page','',0),(281,1,'2013-09-13 19:58:10','2013-09-13 19:58:10','','High Velocity Cooling','','inherit','open','open','','280-revision-v1','','','2013-09-13 19:58:10','2013-09-13 19:58:10','',280,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/280-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(282,1,'2013-09-13 19:58:31','2013-09-13 19:58:31','<h1>Ductless Air Conditioners</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-1077\" title=\"Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air \" alt=\"Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air \" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Blue-Ox-Heating-Air-Back-of-Van-2-300x200.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air understands that keeping your family cool in Minneapolis, MN, is a top priority. Our service professionals also appreciate the fact that every property has unique needs and sometimes a central air conditioning system is not an option.\r\n\r\nWe install ductless air conditioning systems, also referred to as mini-split systems, in homes that require directed air flow without the addition of ducts.\r\n\r\nA ductless air conditioner is comprised of the outside condenser, the indoor unit (which is mounted on the ceiling or wall, or can remain freestanding), and refrigerant lines that connect the two. It is a compact system that is a great choice for any homeowner.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>The Advantages of Ductless Air Conditioners</h2>\r\nIf you live in a home that does not have forced air or use ducts, then a central air conditioning system would probably be prohibitively expensive to install. A ductless air cooling unit offers the following great benefits:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Space Saver</strong> – The compact design of a mini-split system makes them ideal for small spaces like apartments, dorm rooms, attics, master bedrooms or basements.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Conveniently Operated</strong> – Most of the ductless air conditioner units come with a remote control so that complete management of the room’s temperature is always within reach.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Runs Quietly</strong> – A mini-split unit provides comfort with a strong but quiet performance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Ductless Mini Split Systems Are Energy Efficient</h2>\r\nA ductless air conditioning system uses less power than a conventional HVAC unit, saving you money in energy costs. If you use a mini-split system, even in conjunction with a conventional ducted air conditioner, you can have better control over which rooms to cool. Energy efficiency is further increased if you find that you are constantly cooling a space that gets little to no use. It is also valuable if your ducted system inefficiently creates hot spots in one area of the house.\r\n<h2>Contact a Skilled Air Conditioning Tech</h2>\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air is your trusted source for ductless air conditioner installation and repair services. We fully guarantee our work and ensure complete customer satisfaction with every visit. <strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact us</a> today by calling 952-641-0099</strong>.','Ductless Air Conditioners','','publish','open','open','','ductless','','','2013-10-25 16:45:31','2013-10-25 16:45:31','',7,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=282',0,'page','',0),(283,1,'2013-09-13 19:58:31','2013-09-13 19:58:31','','Ductless Cooling','','inherit','open','open','','282-revision-v1','','','2013-09-13 19:58:31','2013-09-13 19:58:31','',282,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/282-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(284,1,'2013-09-13 19:58:42','2013-09-13 19:58:42','<h1>Zone Air Conditioners</h1>\r\n<a href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Zone-Air-Conditioners.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-829\" title=\"Zone Air Conditioners \" alt=\"Zone Air Conditioners \" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/Zone-Air-Conditioners-300x199.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" /></a>Many Minneapolis homeowners don\'t realize that they can save money while making their homes more comfortable by installing zone air conditioning. Zone air conditioners control the temperature in every room, so that homeowners don\'t have to over-cool part of the home to make the temperature in another area merely tolerable.\r\n\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air can help you ensure comfort to every degree by installing a zone cooling system. We always aim for 100% customer satisfaction, and we know that you\'ll love the difference in home atmosphere that a zone air conditioner creates.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How Zone Air Conditioners Work</h2>\r\nZone air conditioners use a <a title=\"Thermostats\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/thermostats/\">thermostat</a> in each room to open or close dampers inside the air conditioning ductwork. These dampers determine the amount of cold air that enters each room. It makes sense to set up separate room thermostats because temperatures can vary between rooms based on many factors, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exposure to sunlight</li>\r\n	<li>Presence of windows and doors</li>\r\n	<li>Level of the house that the room is located on</li>\r\n	<li>Presence of heating appliances or other heat sources</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nZone air conditioning can help homeowners keep the entire house at a consistent temperature. A Zone Air Conditioning Unit is also the best solution for homeowners who want distinct temperatures in different rooms.\r\n<h2>Zone Cooling Helps You Save on Monthly Bills</h2>\r\nHot and humid summers cause many Minneapolis homeowners to spend more than they like on their electric bills. With a zone cooling system, however, you won\'t have to choose between saving money and being comfortable.\r\n\r\nZone air conditioners allow you to cool the rooms that you use and leave the others as they are, reducing energy use. With a typical air conditioning system, you would have to manually close vents in rooms that don\'t need cooling, which is ineffective and can damage your ducts over time. Zone cooling is a much more reliable, cost-effective approach for homeowners who want to keep bills manageable without suffering through summer.\r\n<h2>Start Saving Today</h2>\r\nOnce you begin using zone air conditioning, the energy savings will start offsetting the purchasing price, so there\'s no reason to put off enjoying a better quality of life at home. <strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact Blue Ox</a> by calling 952-647-0099 to get more information or set up an appointment.</strong>','Zone Cooling','','publish','open','open','','zone-cooling','','','2013-10-10 22:50:21','2013-10-10 22:50:21','',7,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=284',0,'page','',0),(285,1,'2013-09-13 19:58:42','2013-09-13 19:58:42','','Zon