><strong>Repair</strong>. The water heater repair services provided by Ben Franklin include repairs for loss of hot water, rusty water, rumbling noises, sulphorous odors, leaking water, and others.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Maintenance</strong>. In order to keep your water heater in good repair at all times, the plumbers at Ben Franklin will provide annual safety inspections, tune-ups, and leak checks. In addition, services and repairs done as a follow up to the inspections receive a 15% discount with a 5% discount on products.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBecause there are different types of water heaters, the professional plumbers at Ben Franklin are experienced and trained to deal with both conventional and tankless heaters.\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started with your water heater repair or replacement today by <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contacting Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air</a> at 952-641-0099.</strong> Let us hook you up with the best services in the industry for water heater issues.','Water Heaters','','publish','open','open','','water-heaters','','','2013-10-25 16:58:28','2013-10-25 16:58:28','',301,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?page_id=329',0,'page','',0),(330,1,'2013-09-13 21:20:04','2013-09-13 21:20:04','','Water Heaters','','inherit','open','open','','329-revision-v1','','','2013-09-13 21:20:04','2013-09-13 21:20:04','',329,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/329-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(332,1,'2013-09-13 21:24:11','2013-09-13 21:24:11',' ','','','publish','open','open','','332','','','2013-10-03 14:27:07','2013-10-03 14:27:07','',0,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?p=332',21,'nav_menu_item','',0),(333,1,'2013-09-13 21:24:11','2013-09-13 21:24:11',' ','','','publish','open','open','','333','','','2013-10-03 14:27:07','2013-10-03 14:27:07','',301,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/?p=333',30,'nav_menu_item','',0),(334,1,'2013-09-13 21:24:11','2013-09-13 21:24:11',' ','','','publish','open','open','','334','','','2013-10-03 14:27:07','2013-10-03 14:27:07','',301,'http://blueox.aigde