ef=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/zone-cooling/\">Zone Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Is My Air Conditioner Inefficient?</h2>\r\nMany homeowners don’t realize that their air conditioning system is inefficient and costing them money. Speak with a Blue Ox representative about new air conditioner installation if you have noticed any of the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>High Energy Bills</strong> – While electricity rates may fluctuate each month, if your energy bills have skyrocketed there may be something wrong with your unit. Our technicians will verify that you are using the correctly sized unit for your property, and take you through a list of possible scenarios that may be the cause of your large power bills. We’ll establish a strategy to fix the issues, and provide you with fast, top of the line AC installation services.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Irregular Cooling</strong> – If one room of the house is sweltering while the other feels like a freezer, your AC is likely operating inefficiently. Your system may need to be rebalanced or replaced. One of our professional HVAC technicians will evaluate the source and address your needs with affordable solutions.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Inadequate Dehumidifying</strong> – When the air in your home feels moist or clammy, your unit is suffering from a significant operational problem. Efficient air conditioners pull moisture from the air; when that doesn’t occur, you may have a dirty unit, insufficient refrigerant charge or an oversized system. A new air conditioner installation may be your best bet to save money and keep your family comfortable.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Top Reasons to Invest in a New Air Conditioner</h2>\r\nIn addition to the overall money you can save by investing in a new, efficient air conditioner, there are additional reasons why you might choose a new unit.\r\n<ol>\r\