 /></a>A <a title=\"Furnaces\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnaces/\">furnace</a> is a long-term investment designed to last many years, but just like any other appliance, it can wear down over time; when it does, Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air can help you with furnace replacement for your old unit. Maintaining a comfortable and healthy home means having an efficient and effective furnace, and the wrong time to wish you had replaced your furnace is when it fails in the middle of a cold Minneapolis winter night.\n\nBlue Ox can help assess your current unit to find out if it needs replacement, and identify the furnace replacement cost as well as the timeline to get a new system. If your system is already damaged, we can help you determine whether it would be more beneficial to repair it or go with furnace replacement.\n<h2>Our Other Heating Services</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li><a title=\"Furnaces\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnaces/\">Furnaces</a></li>\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-repair/\">Furnace Repair</a></li>\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-maintenance/\">Furnace Maintenance</a></li>\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-installation/\">Furnace Installation</a></li>\n	<li><a title=\"Heat Pumps\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/heat-pumps/\">Heat Pumps</a></li>\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Heating\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/zone-heating-cooling/\">Zone Systems</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>When to Repair and When to Replace a Furnace</h2>\nSometimes it can be difficult to know whether you should repair your existing furnace or replace it with a new one. Since furnace replacement costs can be high, many homeowners prefer to pay for repairs, but it’s important to know the warning signs that indicate you need a new furnace:\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Your furnace is old</strong>. Furnaces that are older than 12-15 years