ng an insulated duct system with Blue Ox is the easiest and most cost-effective way to protect your home from these energy losses. Our technicians know what areas of your system are most at risk for energy loss and thus, where ductwork insulation will be most beneficial.\r\n<h2>Put Our Experts to Work for You</h2>\r\nHelp guarantee your HVAC systems energy efficiency by installing an insulated duct system from Blue Ox. Our team promises to put all of our collective resources to work in ensuring that your ductwork insulation is not only keeping you feeling comfortable in your home, but also allowing you to enjoy the extra savings in your energy costs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Call us at 952-647-0099 or <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contact us online</a> to speak with one of our service professionals today.</strong>','Insulated Duct Systems','','inherit','open','open','','321-revision-v1','','','2013-09-19 17:51:26','2013-09-19 17:51:26','',321,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/321-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(510,1,'2013-09-19 17:51:38','2013-09-19 17:51:38','<h1>Plumbing Services by Ben Franklin Minneapolis</h1>\r\nAt Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air, we are so committed to “comfort to every degree” for our customers, that we go out of our way to ensure that your plumbing is taken care of properly. At Blue Ox, we don’t handle those services directly, but have gone out of our way to find you a company with the most highly qualified and experienced professionals in the industry that can tackle your clogged sinks, water heater issues, and more. Our sister company in Minneapolis, Benjamin Franklin, has been repairing leaks and providing outstanding plumbing service for years and they are ready to handle your problem.\r\n<h2>Our Other Services:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Service Plans\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/service-plans/\">Service Plans</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Custom Ductwork\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/ductwork-construction/\">Ductwork Construction</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Insulated Duct Systems\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/ductwork-insulation/\">Insulated Duct Systems</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Thermostats\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/thermostats/\">Thermostats</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Controls\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/controls/\">Controls</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Water Heaters\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/water-heaters/\">Water Heaters</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Plumbing Services by Ben Franklin in Minneapolis</h2>\r\nThe plumbers at Benjamin Franklin in Minneapolis are highly qualified and certified to provide you with the following services and more:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Backflow Testing</strong>. This helps to maintain the quality of potable water and keep it safe for the residents in your area.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Drain Cleaning</strong>. For sinks, showers, bathtubs, toilets, sewer lines, and downspouts. The plumbers at Benjamin Franklin can handle them all.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Garbage Disposal</strong>. Whether your disposal is clogged or broken, the plumbers specialize in repair, replacement, and unclogging.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Leak Detection</strong>. Whether your water bill has been rising, your pipeline burst, or you are always refilling the pool, the plumbers at Benjamin Franklin have the expertise to handle it all.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Maintenance</strong>. This includes safety inspections, leak checks, water heater tune-ups, and more.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Water Softeners</strong>. Water softener installation improves the quality of water in your home, prevents broken pipes, and decreases the amount of pipe clogging.</li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Water Heaters\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/water-heaters/\"><strong>Water Heaters</strong></a>. This plumbing service includes installation, repair, and maintenance for conventional and tankless water heaters.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Contact Us Today</h2>\r\nWhen you contact Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air in Minneapolis, we will ensure that your plumbing needs are taken care of by a professional with the most expertise in the industry. Our sister company, Benjamin Franklin, complies with our commitment to offer each customer “comfort to every degree” and your plumbing service needs will always be taken care of by a professional plumber who values your business.\r\n\r\n<strong>Contact us at 952-647-0099 or through our <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">online contact form</a> to get started today.</strong>','Plumbing','','inherit','open','open','','327-revision-v1','','','2013-09-19 17:51:38','2013-09-19 17:51:38','',327,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/327-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(511,1,'2013-09-19 17:52:05','2013-09-19 17:52:05','<h1>Our Annual Maintenance Program</h1>','Service Plans','','inherit','open','open','','317-revision-v1','','','2013-09-19 17:52:05','2013-09-19 17:52:05','',317,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/317-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(565,1,'2013-09-20 16:18:27','2013-09-20 16:18:27','<h1>Digital &amp; Programmable Thermostats</h1>\r\nYou may love the benefits provided by your HVAC system, but not the constant monitoring that goes into making sure that the temperature inside your home is adequate. Unfortunately, your HVAC system is designed to simply generate hot and cold air, not to recognize when it’s needed. It needs someone calling the shots.\r\n\r\nThat someone is the thermostat. Thermostats may be the most overlooked component of an HVAC system, yet could also be the most important given that they regulate the system’s output. And with a programmable thermostat installed by the professionals at Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air, the job of controlling your HVAC system is done for you. At Blue Ox, we offer a wide variety of programmable digital thermostats to take the away the worry of monitoring your system, allowing you to simply enjoy the comfort that it provides.\r\n<h2>Our Other Services:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Custom Ductwork\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/ductwork-construction/\">Ductwork Construction</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Insulated Duct Systems\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/ductwork-insulation/\">Insulated Duct Systems</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Plumbing\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/plumbing/\">Plumbing</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Water Heaters\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/water-heaters/\">Water Heaters</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>The Advantages of Upgrading Your Thermostat</h2>\r\nIf you’re tired of having to worry about constantly adjusting your thermostat, consider the advantages a programmable one has to offer:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Programming</strong>: You can set your thermostat setting according to time of day, day of week, and date of month. That allows for pre-determined settings that automatically change your HVAC output without you having to worry about it.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Savings</strong>: Programmable thermostats have been shown to save homeowners up to $180 per year based on an annual average of $2,200 in home heating and cooling costs. That more than makes up for their $50 - $100 average initial purchase price.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Design</strong>: Unlike the box-like thermostats that sat as an eyesore on your wall in the past, new programmable thermostats come with backlit display panels that have touchscreen controls.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Digital Thermostats Make Your Life Easier</h2>\r\nDigital thermostats are literally thinking machines that use special thermistors to measure current temperatures compared to preset controls. Whenever the two don’t match, the digital thermostat automatically engages your HVAC system to reach the desired temperature. By taking the few minutes to set up initial programming, you allow the thermostat to monitor and control its own output.\r\n\r\nSo don’t worry abo