his step.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Replace Freon</strong> – Most <a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">air conditioners</a> don’t require the replacement of Freon but it is still important to check the levels to make sure that there is not a leak in the air conditioner.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf your system is performing erratically or you aren’t comfortable with doing systematic air conditioner maintenance on your own, Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air will be pleased to assist you.\r\n<h2>Scheduled AC Maintenance Saves You Time</h2>\r\nAir conditioner emergencies pop up when you least expect them and usually when they are most inconvenient. Regular maintenance of your air conditioning unit keeps you in control of your schedule and helps you catch minor issues before they become a threat to your time and money.\r\n\r\n<strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact Blue Ox</a> by calling 952-647-0099 to schedule your AC maintenance today.</strong>','Air Conditioner Maintenance','','inherit','open','open','','278-revision-v1','','','2013-09-19 18:35:56','2013-09-19 18:35:56','',278,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/278-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(561,1,'2013-09-20 16:17:53','2013-09-20 16:17:53','<h1>Our Other Services</h1>\r\nManaging repairs to your home’s interior can be a daunting process, especially if there are multiple aspects to consider or different systems that need to be addressed. Coordinating with one contractor can be difficult enough; imagine having to do it with three or four!\r\n\r\nThat’s why, at Blue Ox, we realize that in order to truly provide “Comfort to Every Degree,” we can’t be just a one-trick HVAC pony. We’re proud to offer our customers multiple other services when it comes to fixing or replacing components in your home’s heating and cooling systems.\r\n<h2>Other Services We Offer</h2>\r\nIn order to put the finishing touches on our work with your home’s HVAC system, we at Blue Ox also offe