plit unit provides comfort with a strong but quiet performance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Ductless Mini Split Systems Are Energy Efficient</h2>\r\nA ductless air conditioning system uses less power than a conventional HVAC unit, saving you money in energy costs. If you use a mini-split system, even in conjunction with a conventional ducted air conditioner, you can have better control over which rooms to cool. Energy efficiency is further increased if you find that you are constantly cooling a space that gets little to no use. It is also valuable if your ducted system inefficiently creates hot spots in one area of the house.\r\n<h2>Contact a Skilled Air Conditioning Tech</h2>\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air is your trusted source for ductless air conditioner installation and repair services. We fully guarantee our work and ensure complete customer satisfaction with every visit. <strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact us</a> today by calling 952-647-0099</strong>.','Ductless Air Conditioners','','inherit','open','open','','282-revision-v1','','','2013-09-27 19:07:23','2013-09-27 19:07:23','',282,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/282-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(598,1,'2013-09-27 19:08:15','2013-09-27 19:08:15','','stock-photo-8948448-air-condioner-repairman-thumbsup','','inherit','open','open','','stock-photo-8948448-air-condioner-repairman-thumbsup','','','2013-09-27 19:08:15','2013-09-27 19:08:15','',278,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-8948448-air-condioner-repairman-thumbsup.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(645,1,'2013-09-30 19:13:31','2013-09-30 19:13:31','<h1>Seasonal AC Maintenance</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-598\" alt=\"stock-photo-8948448-air-condioner-repairman-thumbsup\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-8948448-air-condioner-repairman-thumbsup-300x199.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" />At Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air we are proud to offer exceptional air conditioner maintenance services to those in Minneapolis, MN, and the Twin Cities area. Annual upkeep of your air conditioner is crucial in order to extend the life of the system and ensure that it is consistently cost-efficient. We strive to preserve our reputation as a company that puts our clients’ comfort first, and our friendly technicians are trained to handle all of your AC maintenance needs.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/zone-cooling/\">Zone Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Air Conditioner Maintenance You Can Do at Home</h2>\r\nWhile routine, professional assessments of your HVAC unit are essential in order to safeguard that your system will effectively operate during the warmer months, proper air conditioner maintenance starts at home. The following tips can be used to help maintain your system:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Change Furnace Filter</strong> – Dirt can build up in the system if the furnace filter is not changed frequently. For those with allergies or asthma, it is best to change the filter every month. A clean filter will promote better air quality and a more efficient system.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Clean Vents</strong> – Warm air is drawn in, cooled, and delivered to your home through the vents. Over time dust will settle on them and should be cleaned off several times a year.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Brush Condenser Coil</strong> – A clean outdoor unit (condenser) produces cooler air while using less energy. Sometime in the spring, use a vacuum, brush or hose to clean the condenser. Contact an AC maintenance technician if you are unsure how to properly perform this step.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf your system is performing erratically or you aren’t comfortable with doing systematic air conditioner maintenance on your own, Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air will be pleased to assist you.\r\n<h2>Scheduled AC Maintenance Saves You Time</h2>\r\nAir conditioner emergencies pop up when you least expect them and usually when they are most inconvenient. Regular maintenance of your air conditioning unit keeps you in control of your schedule and helps you catch minor issues before they become a threat to your time and money.\r\n\r\n<strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact Blue Ox</a> by calling 952-641-0099 to schedule your AC maintenance today.</strong>','Air Conditioner Maintenance','','inherit','open','open','','278-revision-v1','','','2013-09-30 19:13:31','2013-09-30 19:13:31','',278,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/278-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(599,1,'2013-09-27 19:08:22','2013-09-27 19:08:22','<h1>Seasonal AC Maintenance</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-598\" alt=\"stock-photo-8948448-air-condioner-repairman-thumbsup\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-8948448-air-condioner-repairman-thumbsup-300x199.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" />At Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air we are proud to offer exceptional air conditioner maintenance services to those in Minneapolis, MN, and the Twin Cities area. Frequent upkeep of your residential or commercial air conditioner is crucial in order to extend the life of the system and ensure that it is consistently cost-efficient. We strive to preserve our reputation as a company that puts our clients’ comfort first, and our friendly technicians are trained to handle all of your AC maintenance needs, 24/7.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/zone-cooling/\">Zone Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Air Conditioner Maintenance You Can Do at Home</h2>\r\nWhile routine, professional assessments of your HVAC unit are essential in order to safeguard that your system will effectively operate during the warmer months, proper air conditioner maintenance starts at home. The following tips can be used to help maintain your system:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Change Filter</strong> – Dirt can build up in the system if the filters aren’t changed frequently. For those with allergies or asthma, it is best to change the filter every month. For homeowners or businesses without pets, the filter can be replaced every 90 days. A clean filter will promote better air quality and a more efficient system.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Clean Vents</strong> – Warm air is drawn in and cooled through the vents. Over time dust will settle on them and should be cleaned off several times a year.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Brush Condenser Coil</strong> – A clean condenser coil produces cooler air while using less energy. Sometime in the spring, use a vacuum or brush to clean the condenser. Contact an AC maintenance technician if you are unsure how to properly perform this step.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Replace Freon</strong> – Most <a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">air conditioners</a> don’t require the replacement of Freon but it is still important to check the levels to make sure that there is not a leak in the air conditioner.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf your system is performing erratically or you aren’t comfortable with doing systematic air conditioner maintenance on your own, Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air will be pleased to assist you.\r\n<h2>Scheduled AC Maintenance Saves You Time</h2>\r\nAir conditioner emergencies pop up when you least expect them and usually when they are most inconvenient. Regular maintenance of your air conditioning unit keeps you in control of your schedule and helps you catch minor issues before they become a threat to your time and money.\r\n\r\n<strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact Blue Ox</a> by calling 952-647-0099 to schedule your AC maintenance today.</strong>','Air Conditioner Maintenance','','inherit','open','open','','278-revision-v1','','','2013-09-27 19:08:22','2013-09-27 19:08:22','',278,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/278-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(600,1,'2013-09-27 19:23:49','2013-09-27 19:23:49','','stock-photo-11619482-central-air-conditioning','','inherit','open','open','','stock-photo-11619482-central-air-conditioning','','','2013-09-27 19:23:49','2013-09-27 19:23:49','',276,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-11619482-central-air-conditioning.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(601,1,'2013-09-30 19:06:33','2013-09-30 19:06:33','<h1>Expert Air Conditioner Installation</h1>\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-600\" alt=\"stock-photo-11619482-central-air-conditioning\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-pho