ompressor in the outdoor unit is responsible for moving the refrigerant between the coils. Amazingly, this entire process is able to function to bring us the cool and refreshing air that we crave on a hot day.\r\n<h2>Licensed Professionals</h2>\r\nAt Blue Ox Heating and Air, we are proud of our highly-skilled team of professionals. Each technician undergoes a rigorous background check before being hired onto the team. We work hard to uphold our exceptional reputation as being the finest heating and cooling company in the Twin Cities and Minneapolis areas. Let our trained team install your air conditioner units today.\r\n<h2>We Provide Comfort to Every Degree</h2>\r\nAt Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air, we believe that you have the right to feel comfortable in your home. We strive to provide you the best heating and cooling services available. <strong>Call us today at 952-641-0099 or <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contact us online</a> for a free evaluation of your air conditioners.</strong>','Air Conditioners','','inherit','open','open','','272-revision-v1','','','2013-09-30 19:22:54','2013-09-30 19:22:54','',272,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/272-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(649,1,'2013-09-30 19:25:57','2013-09-30 19:25:57','<h1>Ductless Air Conditioners</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-596\" alt=\"stock-photo-9251418-remote-control-and-air-conditioner\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-9251418-remote-control-and-air-conditioner-300x199.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" />Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air understands that keeping your family cool in Minneapolis, MN, is a top priority. Our service professionals also appreciate the fact that every property has unique needs and sometimes a central air conditioning system is not an option.\r\n\r\nWe install ductless air conditioning systems, also referred to as mini-split systems, in homes that require directed air flow without the addition of ducts. A ductless air conditioner is comprised of the outside condenser, the indoor unit (which is mounted on the ceiling or wall, or can remain freestanding), and refrigerant lines that connect the two. It is a compact system that is a great choice for any homeowner.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/zone-cooling/\">Zone Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>The Advantages of Ductless Air Conditioners</h2>\r\nIf you live in a home that does not have forced air or use ducts, then a central air conditioning system would probably be prohibitively expensive to install. A ductless air cooling unit offers the following great benefits:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Space Saver</strong> – The compact design of a mini-split system makes them ideal for small spaces like apartments, dorm rooms, attics, master bedrooms or basements.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Conveniently Operated</strong> – Most of the ductless air conditioner units come with a remote control so that complete management of the room’s temperature is always within reach.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Runs Quietly</strong> – A mini-split unit provides comfort with a strong but quiet performance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Ductless Mini Split Systems Are Energy Efficient</h2>\r\nA ductless air conditioning system uses less power than a conventional HVAC unit, saving you money in energy costs. If you use a mini-split system, even in conjunction with a conventional ducted air conditioner, you can have better control over which rooms to cool. Energy efficiency is further increased if you find that you are constantly cooling a space that gets little to no use. It is also valuable if your ducted system inefficiently creates hot spots in one area of the house.\r\n<h2>Contact a Skilled Air Conditioning Tech</h2>\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air is your trusted source for ductless air conditioner installation and repair services. We fully guarantee our work and ensure complete customer satisfaction with every visit. <strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact us</a> today by calling 952-641-0099</strong>.','Ductless Air Conditioners','','inherit','open','open','','282-revision-v1','','','2013-09-30 19:25:57','2013-09-30 19:25:57','',282,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/282-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(650,1,'2013-09-30 19:32:11','2013-09-30 19:32:11','<h1>High Velocity Air Conditioners</h1>\r\nThe technicians at Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air are experts in the field and understand the intricacies of the weather in Minneapolis, MN, and the Twin Cities area. We keep up to date on the newest systems available and are always prepared to offer property owners the best service possible.\r\n<h2>Our Other Cooling Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/zone-cooling/\">Zone Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How High Velocity Air Conditioning Works</h2>\r\nA high velocity air conditioner draws air over cooling coils instead of pushing it like traditional AC units do. Most mini-duct units use coils with a large surface area which creates colder air currents, thus reducing the costs of running the system while also increasing efficiency.\r\n\r\nConsider the benefits of using a high velocity unit in your property:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Consistent Airflow</strong> – The circulation system of a high velocity AC system is designed to create even airflow in every room of the house. They generally come with many vents that are appropriately placed throughout the property to better facilitate those efforts.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Fast &amp; Efficient</strong> – Using half of the airflow of a conventional AC unit, a high velocity air conditioner can quickly cool a room. They also typically eliminate around 30 percent more of the air’s moisture than a standard system can.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Smaller Ducts</strong> – Mini-duct air conditioners don’t require extensive renovation or bulky ducts. This is a benefit for those who have older homes without an existing central HVAC unit, as well as homeowners who cannot afford the high costs of renovating their home to accommodate them.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Making the Switch to High Velocity Air Conditioning is Easy</h2>\r\nSwitching from a conventional HVAC unit to a mini-duct cooling system is easy. The small ducts are only two inches in diameter and can fit easily inside walls and below floors or other tight spaces. Therefore, it is not necessary to build soffits or creative hiding places to conceal metal ductwork, thus maintaining the integrity of your home.\r\n\r\n<strong><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">Contact Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air</a> today at 952-641-0099 to speak with an air conditioning professional to gain more insight on the benefits of installing a high velocity air conditioner in your home.</strong>','High Velocity Cooling','','inherit','open','open','','280-revision-v1','','','2013-09-30 19:32:11','2013-09-30 19:32:11','',280,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/280-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(652,1,'2013-09-30 20:44:51','2013-09-30 20:44:51','<h1>Brands We Service</h1>\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air not only offers comfort to every degree, we also service brands to every degree. Not every Minneapolis heating and air conditioning company will be able to service your particular brand of <a title=\"Furnaces\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnaces/\">furnace</a> or <a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">air conditioner</a>, and you can spend more time than you might like trying to find one. Rather than calling several repair services and searching for a price you like, make us your first and last call for all of your servicing and repair needs.\r\n<h2>Superior Service</h2>\r\nWe have all of the equipment we need to take care of each residential application, from basic furnaces to cutting edge modulating and variable speed equipment. Specific brands that we service include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mitsubishi</li>\r\n	<li>Carrier</li>\r\n	<li>Coleman</li>\r\n	<li>Trane</li>\r\n	<li>American Standard</li>\r\n	<li>Payne</li>\r\n	<li>LG</li>\r\n	<li>Evcon</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBear in mind that this isn’t even a full list of the air conditioner and heating brands that Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air services. We can actually service any time of brand to the highest standards, so please don’t assume that just because you don’t see your particular brand listed that we’re unable to service it. It’s always best that you call us beforehand so that one of our highly trained consultants can see just what they can do for you.\r\n\r\n<strong>If your unit is malfunctioning, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contact Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air</a> by calling us at 952-641-0099.</strong>','Brands We Service','','inherit','open','open','','246-revision-v1','','','2013-09-30 20:44:51','2013-09-30 20:44:51','',246,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/246-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(653,1,'2013-09-30 20:45:39','2013-09-30 20:45:39','<h1>About Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air</h1>\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air is a full-service residential heating and air conditioning company that also specializes in <a title=\"Air Quality\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/\">air quality</a> products and services. We are fully licensed, bonded, and insured to provide our Minneapolis customers with services relating to furnaces, heating, and air conditioning. We are NATE certified and a member of the Minnesota Heating &amp; Cooling Association. Our heating and air conditioning company provides sales, installation, and repair for any number of heating, cooling, and air quality units and parts.\r\n<h2>Why Choose Our HVAC Company?</h2>\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air was started in July 2013. Although we are a new heating and air conditioning company, we are not new to the field of heating, ventilation, and air conditioning (HVAC). In fact, our company has many years of cumulative experience, approaching more than 200 combined years of work in heating and air conditioning. That means you can trust Blue Ox with your home comfort. Our technicians are background checked, wear shoe covers while in your home, do not use bad language, and do not use tobacco while on the job.\r\n<h2>Comfort to Every Degree</h2>\r\nWith many other service providers available in the area, why should you choose us?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our staff truly cares about the happiness of our clients.</li>\r\n	<li>Our services are 100% satisfaction guaranteed or we will cheerfully refund your money.</li>\r\n	<li>We know that satisfaction with your heating company or air conditioning company means more than just keeping your home at the right temperature. It means quality heating products, great service, low prices.</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that if you are truly pleased with our services and products in every way, you will have no need to go anywhere else for your HVAC needs.</li>\r\n	<li>At Blue Ox, we provide our customers with “Comfort to Every Degree.”</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>We are happy to serve our neighbors and friends in the Minneapolis area. Call Blue Ox today at 952-647-0099 or <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contact us online</a> for service.</strong>','About','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2013-09-30 20:45:39','2013-09-30 20:45:39','',5,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(654,1,'2013-09-30 20:46:55','2013-09-30 20:46:55','<h1>Indoor Air Quality Services</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-625\" alt=\"stock-photo-26961605-removing-air-filter\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-26961605-removing-air-filter-300x287.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"287\" />When most people think of potential health risks, they typically don\'t think of poor indoor air quality. However, air quality is not just a concern for people living in crowded cities and industrial centers. As a Minneapolis homeowner, you are also at risk of suffering from the effects of poor home air quality.\r\n\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air can provide you with air quality services and solutions. We can help you with everything from choosing a product to installation. Whether you\'re concerned with allergy prevention or pollutant removal, we have a number of products that can help you.\r\n<h2>Home Air Quality Products to Improve Health</h2>\r\nThere are various ways to improve air quality throughout your home, which can prevent allergy symptoms and respiratory illnesses. We offer the following proven air quality products:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Humidifiers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/humidifiers/\">Humidifiers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Dehumidifiers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/dehumidifiers/\">Dehumidifiers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Purifiers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/air-purifiers/\">Air Purifiers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Exchangers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/air-exchangers/\">Air Exchangers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"HEPA\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/hepa-filters/\">HEPA Filters</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"UV Lights\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/uv-lights/\">UV Lights</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe whole-home systems that we offer are much more effective at allergy prevention and health protection than individual units that clean the air in one room. Only a centralized system allows you to reach and treat all of the air in your home.\r\n<h2>Indoor Air Quality Facts That Might Shock You</h2>\r\nMany people do not realize how harmful poor home air quality can be. According to the American Lung Association, poor air quality indoors can cause headaches, exhaustion, nausea, asthma, lung infections, and even lung cancer. The Environmental Protection Agency, meanwhile, reports these disturbing facts about indoor air quality:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Indoor air can contain two to five times the pollutants than that of outdoor air.</li>\r\n	<li>Pollutant concentrations can be even greater because of high temperatures, humidity, and poor ventilation.</li>\r\n	<li>The average American passes nine out of ten hours indoors.</li>\r\n	<li>One of the five worst environmental health risks is indoor air pollution.</li>\r\n	<li>Pollutants can be worse for children because children breathe more air relative to their size.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMany homeowners never suspect the dangers of poor home air quality. Given how much time a typical person spends inside, it is clear that keeping indoor air quality high is a real health concern.\r\n<h2>Call Us Today</h2>\r\nDon\'t delay bringing the air in your home up to healthy standards. Poor air quality can lead to serious problems if you live with it long enough. <strong>You can learn more about the various air quality products that we offer by calling Blue Ox at 952-641-0099 or <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contacting us online</a>.</strong>','Air Quality','','inherit','open','open','','303-revision-v1','','','2013-09-30 20:46:55','2013-09-30 20:46:55','',303,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/303-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(655,1,'2013-10-01 18:24:36','2013-10-01 18:24:36','<h1>Professional Heating Services</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-617\" alt=\"stock-photo-11070678-happy-family-at-home\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-11070678-happy-family-at-home-300x199.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" />Your home is the place where you go to feel safe, warm, and cozy, but when your furnace is not working, a home can be anything but comforting. At Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air we offer a full range of professional heating services, including furnace repair, furnace maintenance and furnace replacement for homes in Minneapolis and the surrounding area.\r\n\r\nWe only hire the best technicians, so you can have peace of mind knowing that all our expert techs have passed a background check, and are fully licensed and insured. We are a local company that provides heating and cooling repair and replacement services here in the community, and we stand behind the work that we do because we hire the best people, keep them up to date with the latest trends in heating and cooling technology, and equip them with the best tools to diagnose and repair any problems.\r\n<h2>Our Heating Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\