ovide warmth and comfort for your family.</strong>','Heating','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-v1','','','2013-10-01 18:24:36','2013-10-01 18:24:36','',6,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/6-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(659,1,'2013-10-01 18:36:46','2013-10-01 18:36:46','<h1>Furnace Replacement Services</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-613\" alt=\"stock-photo-16637459-repair-technician-removing-furnace-service-panel\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-16637459-repair-technician-removing-furnace-service-panel-300x208.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"208\" />A <a title=\"Furnaces\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnaces/\">furnace</a> is a long-term investment designed to last many years, but just like any other appliance, it can wear down over time; when it does, Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air can help you with furnace replacement for your old unit. Maintaining a comfortable and healthy home means having an efficient and effective furnace, and the wrong time to wish you had replaced your furnace is when it fails in the middle of a cold Minneapolis winter night.\r\n\r\nBlue Ox can help assess your current unit to find out if it needs replacement, and identify the furnace replacement cost as well as the timeline to get a new system. If your system is already damaged, we can help you determine whether it would be more beneficial to repair it or go with furnace replacement.\r\n<h2>Our Other Heating Services</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnaces\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnaces/\">Furnaces</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-repair/\">Furnace Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-maintenance/\">Furnace Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-installation/\">Furnace Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Heat Exchangers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/heat-exchangers/\">Heat Exchangers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Heat Pumps\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/heat-pumps/\">Heat Pumps</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Heating\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/zone-heating/\">Zone Heating</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>When to Repair and When to Replace a Furnace</h2>\r\nSometimes it can be difficult to know whether you should repair your existing furnace or replace it with a new one. Since furnace replacement costs can be high, many homeowners prefer to pay for repairs, but it’s important to know the warning signs that indicate you need a new furnace:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Your furnace is old</strong>. Furnaces that are older than 12-15 years are likely inefficient, and should be replaced before a major problem occurs.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Your monthly utility bills are increasing</strong>. Higher utility bills often indicate an inefficient system that has to run longer to provide the same amount of heat.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>The thermostats are inconsistent</strong>. If you are constantly adjusting the thermostat to try and find the right temperature, the furnace may not be distributing air properly.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>You are spending a lot on repairs</strong>. As a furnace ages, the costs to repair can be expensive, and frequent. Instead of spending more money to repair an inefficient and old furnace, consider getting a new one.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Your furnace is making noises</strong>. While all furnaces make a little bit of noise, excessive noise or strange sounds like banging, popping, and rattling can indicate a problem.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Professional Repairs Offered 24 Hours a Day</h2>\r\nBlue Ox Heating &amp; Air hires only the highest quality technicians to replace your old furnace. We offer 24-hour repair services for emergency situations and can come to your house any time of the day or night that you experience problems with your furnace. You can rest assured when you hire Blue Ox that our technicians will provide the highest level of customer service and professionalism. Every member of our team has passed a background check and has the proper training and experience to quickly diagnose and resolve issues with all types of furnaces, no matter what time of the day or night.\r\n\r\n<strong>Don’t wait for your old furnace to quit, <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contact us</a> today at 952-641-0099 to get a brand new, energy efficient furnace installed by our team of trained furnace replacement professionals.</strong>','Furnace Replacement','','inherit','open','open','','259-revision-v1','','','2013-10-01 18:36:46','2013-10-01 18:36:46','',259,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/259-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(662,1,'2013-10-01 18:45:28','2013-10-01 18:45:28','<h1>Residential Air Conditioning &amp; Heating Company in Minneapolis</h1>\r\nWelcome to Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air! As your full service residential heating and air conditioning company in Minneapolis, our top priority is to make sure that your home’s physical environment meets your comfort needs.\r\n<h2>Our Heating Services</h2>\r\nBlue Ox is a heating company that offers a comprehensive array of services. We are fully licensed, bonded and insured to perform service on heating and cooling systems and components. We are more than a furnace repair company. Our heating services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnaces\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnaces/\">Furnaces</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-repair/\">Furnace Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Replacement\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-replacement/\">Furnace Replacement</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-maintenance/\">Furnace Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Furnace Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/furnace-installation/\">Furnace Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Heat Exchangers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/heat-exchangers/\">Heat Exchangers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Heat Pumps\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/heat-pumps/\">Heat Pumps</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Heating\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/hvac/zone-heating/\">Zone Heating</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Our Air Conditioning Services</h2>\r\nWe also provide services as a comprehensive air conditioning company. Our air conditioning services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioners\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioners/\">Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Repair\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-repair/\">Air Conditioner Repair</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Installation\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-installation/\">Air Conditioner Installation</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Conditioner Maintenance\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/air-conditioner-maintenance/\">Air Conditioner Maintenance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"High Velocity Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/high-velocity-air-conditioners/\">High Velocity Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Ductless Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/ductless/\">Ductless Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Zone Cooling\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/ac-service/zone-cooling/\">Zone Air Conditioners</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAll of our services are performed by polite, background checked individuals who are certified and experienced in the field of air conditioning. Our technicians wear shoe covers, and do not smoke or use offensive language while providing services in the homes of our clients.\r\n<h2>Our Other Services</h2>\r\nBlue Ox also provides services relating to:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Quality\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/\">Indoor Air Quality</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Humidifiers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/humidifiers/\">Humidifiers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Dehumidifiers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/dehumidifiers/\">Dehumidifiers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Purifiers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/air-purifiers/\">Air Purifiers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Air Exchangers\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/air-exchangers/\">Air Exchangers</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"HEPA\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/hepa-filters/\">HEPA Filters</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"UV Lights\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/indoor-air-quality/uv-lights/\">UV Lights</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Custom Ductwork\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/ductwork-construction/\">Ductwork Construction</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Thermostats\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/thermostats/\">Thermostats</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe accept payment in the form of cash, check, or credit card. We also offer 0% financing on approved credit.\r\n<h2>“Comfort To Every Degree”</h2>\r\nWe are confident in our ability to provide service you will be happy with. With Blue Ox there is no risk because our services are backed by a 100% Satisfaction or Money Back Guarantee!\r\n\r\nThough the temperature of your home is important in regards to HVAC services, we understand that there is much more to consider when it comes to your comfort. We truly believe that we can provide service that will satisfy your physical, financial, and air quality comfort needs, as well as delivering high quality, efficient work. That’s why here at Blue Ox, our motto is “Comfort To Every Degree!”\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;\">Call us at 952-641-0099 or <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contact us online</a> to schedule service with our heating and air conditioning company today.</span></strong>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','91-revision-v1','','','2013-10-01 18:45:28','2013-10-01 18:45:28','',91,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/91-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(664,1,'2013-10-01 18:49:58','2013-10-01 18:49:58','<h1>Ductwork Construction Services</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-615\" alt=\"stock-photo-12354020-worker-installing-an-hvac-air-duct\" src=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/images/stock-photo-12354020-worker-installing-an-hvac-air-duct-199x300.jpg\" width=\"199\" height=\"300\" />An HVAC system’s efficiency is largely determined on how it fits within a home. Installing a system that is not fit to the unique aspects of your home can be like trying to hammer a square peg into a round hole, and can ultimately cost you up to 40% of the system’s designed efficiency.\r\n\r\nThe ductwork is the backbone of your home’s HVAC system, delivering air from your air conditioner or furnace. It’s this stage of the home heating and cooling process that most influences your system’s energy efficiency. That’s why Blue Ox Heating &amp; Air offers services in custom ductwork fitting to ensure that your system matches your structure. We do our own ductwork construction after determining how and where tubing and connections will run within your home.\r\n<h2>Our Other Services:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Insulated Duct Systems\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/ductwork-insulation/\">Insulated Duct Systems</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Thermostats\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/thermostats/\">Thermostats</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Plumbing\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/plumbing/\">Plumbing</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Water Heaters\" href=\"http://blueox.aigdev.net/other-services/water-heaters/\">Water Heaters</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>How Custom Ductwork Saves You Money</h2>\r\nAt Blue Ox, we have over 200 years of combined experience in meeting the HVAC needs of the Twin Cities residents. That experience has taught us that a majority of your heating and cooling savings come from not wasting energy by pushing more air through your system to compensate for its design inadequacies.\r\n\r\nThese factors illustrate that point:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Size</strong>: Imagine yourself trying to blow air through a length of PVC pipe. Odds are not much is coming out of the other end. Now imagine doing the same thing with a straw, and you can picture the difference. Ductwork is much the same. Ducts that are too large require more energy to push the air through the system.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Special Connections</strong>: Most energy is lost at junctions in your network of ducts, be it at the plenum, distribution box, or the register. Making sure that these connective ducts fit the contours of the areas they’re placed in helps to cut down on the amount of air lost.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBy allowing us to outfit your home’s HVAC system with custom ductwork, you can avoid the financial pitfalls that can come with choosing a “one-size-fits-all” system not designed to meet your specific heating and cooling needs.\r\n<h2>Trust Us to Help You</h2>\r\nPut our experience in manufacturing custom ductwork to work for you in outfitting your home’s HVAC system. We guarantee that our ductwork construction is second to none, and you’ll feel the results in the new-found comfort you have in your home.\r\n\r\n<strong>Call us at 952-641-0099 or <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"/contact-us/\">contact us online</a> to schedule an appointment with one of our HVAC technicians today.</strong>','Custom Ductwork','','inherit','open','open','','319-revision-v1','','','2013-10-01 18:49:58','2013-10-01 18:49:58','',319,'http://blueox.aigdev.net/319-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(668,1,'2013-10-01 19:45:01','2013-10-01 19:45:01','<h1>Water Heater Services</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-590\" title=\"Ben Franklin Water Heater Service\" alt=\"Ben Franklin Water Heate